</paragraph>
<paragraph id="D36136DFFFE2FFE8FF5DFC23FC908B9A" blockId="6.[151,1437,562,1036]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">
<emphasis id="E1AAEACDFFE2FFE8FF5DFC23FE5E8BBC" bold="true" box="[196,462,935,961]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">General distribution:</emphasis>
An eastern species ranging from Massachusetts south to Florida, west to Louisiana and Texas, and in the Midwest from Ohio to Kansas.
</paragraph>
